[{"Id": 1015858, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 1, "EnglishDescription": "It is recommended that a pilgrim continues this humble prayer slowly with full devotion and concentration on Allah. Recite the following with other supplications while performing circumambulation. Imam Sadiq (a) said: While circumambulating, recite <Dua-e-Tawaaf>.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Tawaaf ke dauraan haaji ke liye mukammal khuloos aur bhar-pur tawajjoh ke saath har tawaaf mein apne Ma’bood ki baargah mein aahista aahista (dhime dhime) raaz o neyaaz aur dua o munajaat karte rehna mustahab hai. Har tawaaf ki makhsoos dua ke alaawa woh yeh <Dua-e-Tawaaf> bhi padh sakta hai jo Imam Sadiq (a) ne farmaaya hai.", "UrduDescription": "طواف کے دوران حاجی کے لئے مکمل خلوص اور بھرپور توجہ کے ساتھ ہر شوط (چکّر) میں اپنے معبود کی بارگاہ میں آہستہ آہستہ راز و نیاز اور دُعا و مناجات کرتے رہنا مستحب ہے۔ ہر شوط کی مخصوص دُعا کے علاوہ امام جعفر صادقؑ کی تاکید کردہ یہ <دُعاء طواف> بھی پڑھ سکتے ہے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": nu